ation\nregion. We show numerical examples of vectorial Slepian functions on the ball,\nwhich demonstrate the good localisation of these functions and the accurate\nestimate of the Shannon number.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jul 2017 07:26:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-11"}
